      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、やっぱりロビーに\nまだいるみたいだね",
      "startTime": 3.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "こころ達に休めって言うなら\n自分も部屋で休んでいてくれればいいのに……",
      "startTime": 8.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.4035372734
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "本当にうまくいくかな？\n外に出るのはロビーを通るしかないんだよね？",
      "startTime": 14.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.3702039401
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "二人であれだけ考えたんですから\nなんとかなりますって～",
      "startTime": 20.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.1784804026
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、すみれちゃん。映画の主人公になった気分で\nこころ達は、凄腕のスパイですよ……！",
      "startTime": 27.0530156608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.5971198717
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったね。私はスパイ、スパイ……\nこちら、ヴァイオレット。いつでも大丈夫です",
      "startTime": 36.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.3637865383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "お、いいですね。それじゃあこころも……\nこちらハート。覚悟は決まったようだな",
      "startTime": 43.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.6442400295
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "それでは早速、作戦を実行に移すとしよう\n手はず通りに動くように",
      "startTime": 51.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.7175731021
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "まずは作戦その一。物陰に隠れながらロビーの\n出口を目指す大作戦……開始だ！",
      "startTime": 57.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.1062590914
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cart-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 61.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.8000012715
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "隠れられる場所……シーツを乗せた台車が\nちょうど近くを通り掛かりそうです。オーバー",
      "startTime": 66.5333346049,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cart-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9599.998728399996,
          "startTime": 76.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.7395924248
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "すぐ隣にいるのにオーバーは必要なのか\n分からないが、了解した。オーバー",
      "startTime": 72.5769033,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9023.097971500007,
          "startTime": 81.6000012715
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.6108166374
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "前を通り過ぎるタイミングで隠れさせてもらおう\nゆっくりと、足音を立てないように……",
      "startTime": 79.5333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.4333346049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "無事に隠れられたね。向こうからはちょうど\n死角になってて見えてないみたい",
      "startTime": 88.9666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.9318583803
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ。このまま無事に外に出ることが出来たら\nどんなわくわくが待ってるんでしょうかね～",
      "startTime": 96.5333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.0381165819
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "口調が崩れてきてるよ、こころちゃん\n……あ、そろそろ出口が見えてきた――",
      "startTime": 103.4333346049,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2538.1193792999993,
          "startTime": 105.9714539842
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5133.333333300001,
          "startTime": 108.5666679382
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.4333346049
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.9714539842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、すみれ。二人ともこんな所で\n何をしているんだ？",
      "startTime": 109.0666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.7714539842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃあ！？　{user}さん！？\nな、なんで？　ちゃんと隠れてたのに",
      "startTime": 113.2333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.0381206509
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "シーツの上から、こころのツノが飛び出しているのが\n見えていたんだが……「隠れてた」……？",
      "startTime": 120.4000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.9714539842
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "くっ、やられました……！　まさかこころの\n可愛いこだわりが仇になるとは……！",
      "startTime": 128.8333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……随分と挙動が怪しいようだが\nさては何か企んでいるな？",
      "startTime": 134.1333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.8617939309
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "た、企んでなんていませんよ。ちょっと喉が渇いたので\n何か飲み物でも買いに行こうかな～って",
      "startTime": 142.1666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "外に出ようとしてたのか？\nホテルの中にも自販機はあるだろう？",
      "startTime": 148.6000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.1097081498
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "ほしい物が売ってなかったんですよね～\n大阪にしかない限定品でして～",
      "startTime": 154.5000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。すまない、そういえば差し入れとか用意して\nなかったよな。俺が買って来るよ、なんて飲み物だ？",
      "startTime": 162.4000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.2443627036
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_02-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "……えっと、なんでしたっけ～？\nすみれちゃん、思い出せます？",
      "startTime": 171.3666679382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.7978998816
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
